[38;5;252m[1m## Summary[0m[0m
[0m[0m
Drafted [38;5;10mchapter10.08-voice-biomarker-detection.md[0m (~161 KB) covering voice biomarker detection in healthcare. The recipe follows the Cookbook Mode structure used by Chapter 1 and recipe 10.7:[0m[0m
[0m[0m
- **The Problem**: opens with the Parkinson's-detectable-thirty-seconds vignette, walks through the seductive promise of voice biomarkers, and lays out the five reasons the gap between marketing and clinical reality is wide (clinical validation, regulatory, demographic equity, recording quality, reproducibility).[0m[0m
- **The Technology**: vendor-agnostic teaching of what voice tells you about a body (vocal fold function, speech timing, prosody, articulation, respiratory sounds, cognitive features, affect), the engineered-vs-deep-learning-vs-hybrid feature pipeline, validation discipline (speaker-disjoint splits, confound control, per-cohort reporting, pre-registration, prospective validation, post-market surveillance), and where the field has moved.[0m[0m
- **General Architecture Pattern**: 8-stage ASCII pipeline (capture protocol/consent, audio capture/QA, preprocessing/feature extraction, per-indication scoring, confidence/confound assessment, clinical-interpretation packaging, clinician review, longitudinal storage/post-market monitoring) plus cross-cutting design points (voice-as-biometric, indication-specific validation, eligibility checking, indeterminate as first-class output, per-cohort calibration, workflow placement, longitudinal trajectory, post-market surveillance built-in).[0m[0m
- **AWS Implementation**: SageMaker (real-time + Async + Model Monitor + Clarify), Transcribe Medical, Comprehend Medical, Bedrock + Guardrails, HealthLake, with full Mermaid architecture diagram, Prerequisites, Ingredients, 7-step pseudocode walkthrough, Expected Results with sample JSON and benchmarks table, "Where it struggles," "Why This Isn't Production-Ready," The Honest Take, Variations, Related Recipes, Resources, time estimates, tags, and navigation.[0m[0m
